764
00:38:14,250 --> 00:38:15,291
Are you okay, man?

765
00:38:15,375 --> 00:38:16,583
Yeah, thanks.

766
00:38:16,666 --> 00:38:17,916
[MALE ONLOOKER B]
That was really close.

767
00:38:18,000 --> 00:38:19,458
[FEMALE ONLOOKER B]
We all could have died!

768
00:38:19,541 --> 00:38:20,666
[MALE ONLOOKER C] If that had
fallen a little to the left.

769
00:38:20,750 --> 00:38:21,875
[FEMALE ONLOOKER C]
It really is a miracle!

770
00:38:21,958 --> 00:38:23,708
[MALE ONLOOKER D]
Yeah, it's a miracle!

771
00:38:23,791 --> 00:38:25,250
[MALE ONLOOKER E] A miracle!

772
00:38:27,625 --> 00:38:30,958
[water drops]

773
00:38:31,041 --> 00:38:32,416
Mmm.

774
00:38:35,583 --> 00:38:38,625
Uuuh...

775
00:38:38,708 --> 00:38:42,916
Wake up! Get off me,
will you? Come on!

776
00:38:55,791 --> 00:38:59,583
[SHUTAURA] Meigo wasn't
