778
00:39:02,458 --> 00:39:04,458
Very well. Carry on, then.

779
00:39:04,541 --> 00:39:06,250
[beeps]

780
00:39:07,291 --> 00:39:09,916
[KAMIJO groans]

781
00:39:10,000 --> 00:39:12,041
[SHUTAURA]
Are you finally awake?

782
00:39:12,125 --> 00:39:13,083
Where are we?

783
00:39:13,166 --> 00:39:14,041
[whimpers]

784
00:39:14,125 --> 00:39:15,750
Don't move
around too much.

785
00:39:20,041 --> 00:39:23,250
[KAMIJO] Wait, are they okay?
Arisa and the others?

786
00:39:23,333 --> 00:39:25,291
They're safe.

787
00:39:25,375 --> 00:39:26,916
Your friend
is just fine,

788
00:39:27,000 --> 00:39:28,708
