00:41:07,583 --> 00:41:09,250
There have been
reports of an explosion

833
00:41:09,333 --> 00:41:10,750
in the facility
underneath the mall,

834
00:41:10,833 --> 00:41:13,416
but the exact cause is
still under investigation.

835
00:41:13,500 --> 00:41:14,875
The city is shaken.

836
00:41:14,958 --> 00:41:17,000
At the time of the bombing,
a live event was underway

837
00:41:17,083 --> 00:41:18,375
for the singer Arisa,

838
00:41:18,458 --> 00:41:20,625
and yet there was not
a single fatality reported.

839
00:41:20,708 --> 00:41:21,916
[MAN C] It's a miracle.
A real miracle!

840
00:41:22,000 --> 00:41:22,958
[YOUNG GIRL A]
They say it was a miracle.

841
00:41:23,041 --> 00:41:24,250
[YOUNG GIRL B]
Yeah, a miracle!

842
00:41:24,333 --> 00:41:25,333
[WOMAN A] A miracle?

843
00:41:25,416 --> 00:41:26,458
[MAN C]
Arisa is a miracle maker!

844
00:41:26,541 --> 00:41:27,541
[WOMAN A] It's a miracle!

845
00:41:27,625 --> 00:41:29,208
[MAN C] A miracle!

846
00:41:30,666 --> 00:41:33,875
[CROWD chatter]

847
00:41:33,958 --> 00:41:36,625
[footsteps]

848
00:41:36,708 --> 00:41:38,083
[KAMIJO] Are you all right?

849
00:41:38,166 --> 00:41:39,541
Huh?

850
00:41:41,250 --> 00:41:42,916
[ARISA] Toma.

851
00:41:45,041 --> 00:41:47,000
[ARISA] It doesn't
seem right, does it?

852
00:41:47,083 --> 00:41:49,375
I mean, if it
really was a miracle...

853
00:41:49,458 --> 00:41:50,666
well, wouldn't
the whole incident

854
00:41:50,750 --> 00:41:52,875
