in the first place?

855
00:41:52,958 --> 00:41:55,250
You know, you
might have a point.

856
00:41:57,208 --> 00:42:00,375
[ARISA] This could be
turning into a pattern.

857
00:42:00,458 --> 00:42:01,916
Apparently I was
involved in another

858
