862
00:42:09,625 --> 00:42:10,791
[gasps]

863
00:42:10,875 --> 00:42:12,541
My name was given to
me by someone who was

864
00:42:12,625 --> 00:42:15,791
working for the facility that
took me in after the accident.

865
00:42:15,875 --> 00:42:18,791
[ARISA] So, I don't have
anything that I can call my own.

866
00:42:18,875 --> 00:42:21,125
But when I'm singing, I don't
care about any of that.

867
00:42:21,208 --> 00:42:22,958
I know exactly who I am.

868
00:42:23,041 --> 00:42:25,541
And then I don't
feel so lonely anymore.

869
00:42:25,625 --> 00:42:27,583
As long as I have my
songs, I feel like I can

870
00:42:27,666 --> 00:42:32,041
recover what I lost. Like
someday I'll be whole again.

871
00:42:32,125 --> 00:42:33,791
I understand what you're
going through more than

872
00:42:33,875 --> 00:42:36,375
you may realize. And I
think you're really lucky

873
00:42:36,458 --> 00:42:39,375
to have something you
believe in so passionately.

874
00:42:40,208 --> 00:42:43,250
[KAMIJO] Don't worry.
It'll turn out all right.

875
00:42:45,291 --> 00:42:47,166
[FEMALE INTERVIEWER]
Endymion's unveiling ceremony

876
00:42:47,250 --> 00:42:49,875
is coming up in two days,
isn't that right?

877
00:42:49,958 --> 00:42:52,583
Yes. We are more than
ready to show the results

878
00:42:52,666 --> 00:42:54,125
of our years of hard work.

879
00:42:54,208 --> 00:42:56,041
[LADYLEE] I have no doubt that
our company will once again

880
00:42:56,125 --> 00:42:58,625
help the world see what
a true miracle looks like!

881
00:42:58,708 --> 00:43:02,500
[cheering]
[music begins]

