897
00:44:02,333 --> 00:44:03,750
Wouldn't you agree?

898
00:44:03,833 --> 00:44:06,000
No. It all sounds
like noise to me,

899
00:44:06,083 --> 00:44:07,500
and I don't
believe in miracles.

900
00:44:07,583 --> 00:44:09,833
You know, you have a
very unpleasant disposition.

901
00:44:09,916 --> 00:44:11,500
[LADYLEE] There is one thing
and one thing only that has

902
00:44:11,583 --> 00:44:14,000
kept Orbit Portal
thriving instead of crashing

