00:44:14,083 --> 00:44:15,791
into the ground
like the Orion did,

904
00:44:15,875 --> 00:44:18,666
and that is the legend of
the Miracle of the Eighty-eight.

905
00:44:18,750 --> 00:44:22,625
In a sense, miracles are our
company's greatest commodity.

906
00:44:22,708 --> 00:44:25,166
What happened on the Orion
was by no means a miracle--

907
00:44:25,250 --> 00:44:26,583
A plane fell from outer space,

908
00:44:26,666 --> 00:44:28,250
and eighty-eight
people survived.

909
00:44:28,333 --> 00:44:30,458
[LADYLEE] If that isn't a
miracle, then what is it?

910
00:44:30,541 --> 00:44:35,416
[ARISA'S song continues]

911
00:44:35,500 --> 00:44:38,458
It won't be long now.
Everything is in order.

912
00:44:38,541 --> 00:44:40,958
[LADYLEE] All of our
preparations are complete.

913
00:44:41,583 --> 00:44:43,708
It's almost time.
Are you ready?

914
00:44:43,791 --> 00:44:44,916
Mhmm.

915
00:44:45,000 --> 00:44:46,416
I want to thank
you for helping me.

916
00:44:46,500 --> 00:44:47,875
I couldn't have
done it without you.

917
00:44:47,958 --> 00:44:50,041
Today is my treat,
so order whatever you want.

918
00:44:50,125 --> 00:44:51,125
Anything at all!

919
00:44:51,208 --> 00:44:53,416
[INDEX] Really?
Oh, waitress! Over here!

920
00:44:53,500 --> 00:44:55,333
Sure, coming!

921
00:44:55,416 --> 00:44:58,083
