00:45:11,666 --> 00:45:13,291
[KAMIJO] Kanzaki!

930
00:45:13,375 --> 00:45:15,375
[KANZAKI] She's provisionally
ranked ninth, but if she was

931
00:45:15,458 --> 00:45:17,625
