even stronger than I am.

933
00:45:19,791 --> 00:45:21,125
[KAMIJO] Arisa Meigo's a saint?

934
00:45:21,208 --> 00:45:22,708
[TSUCHIMIKADO] That's
still just supposition.

935
00:45:22,791 --> 00:45:24,000
Call it our working theory.

936
00:45:24,083 --> 00:45:26,166
