[SHUTAURA] Come in Crow 4,
this is Crow Leader. Sitrep.

972
00:46:44,375 --> 00:46:46,750
[CROW 4] Currently pursuing
target on the expressway.

973
00:46:48,250 --> 00:46:49,916
[SHUTAURA] Don't lose them.

974
00:46:52,333 --> 00:46:54,333
[SHUTAURA] There's no
such thing as a miracle.

975
00:46:56,250 --> 00:46:58,291
And I'm going to prove it.

976
00:46:58,375 --> 00:47:00,333
[car horn honks]

977
00:47:00,416 --> 00:47:02,041
[JANE] Um, excuse me, Master?

978
00:47:02,125 --> 00:47:03,416
[STIYL] Hmm?

979
00:47:03,500 --> 00:47:05,166
